    "For instance, the values 10, 7, 3, 0.5, and 0 are often used for perfect, excellent, good, fair, and bad results, respectively 37.",
    "If there are several search queries to be evaluated, mean DCG can be used.",
    "The motivation behind statistical tests is often to find out whether there is a significant difference between two different populations within respect of some specific property.",
    "We can collect smaller data sets from the populations and use them to compute values of the numeric quantity representing the feature of interest.",
